{"tid":354694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱第一次試用Gobee Bike 結果......","createTime":"2017-08-10T16:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T13:16:02.000Z","uid":39081,"like":7,"dislike":529,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3eb0feb7dd72bca992563d1d230ddc236ab3340","tid":354694,"uid":39081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱同班fd係沙田食完飯<br />\n其中一兩個都住馬鞍山嘅<br />\n咁就一齊走啦<br />\n點知佢地今日踩單車出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁無理由咁戇鳩<br />\n佢地踩單車 我行路㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咁就獻出我第一次<br />\n試吓用Gobee Bike啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身都無抱太大期望<br />\n但踩落又覺得都算幾好踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係除咗上斜無得轉波比較辛苦啲之外<br />\n走平路 落斜都好順<br />\n咁多位巴絲有機會 又未試過嘅都可以試吓<br />\n第一次用仲可以入Promotion Code免你半個鐘錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而無Promotion Code嘅巴絲<br />\n又想免半個鐘錢嘅話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就不況用我下面呢嗰呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一家便宜兩家著嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPromotion Code : <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1wnlXV</span></span>"},{"pid":"04fc4fc02f524294ee3cdd7ef57cf48ac6c8ab4c","tid":354694,"uid":39081,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"做咩要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2977abd15364b31175e714155cecfa8d1c4b3869","tid":354694,"uid":15309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4889836c4912f84024d9646cc708d96e2e88f7c4","tid":354694,"uid":39081,"like":3,"dislike":27,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:23:37.000Z","msg":